<p id="HEADLINE">BSD Make Pallàs Scripts</p>
<p id="INTRODUCTION"><p>BSD Make Pallàs Scripts is a group of BSD Make template files. They
are written mich in the spirit of FreeBSD's Make template files, with
portability in mind: they can also be used on GNU/Linux systems, Mac
OS X and Sun Solaris. Currently available scripts may be used for
OCaml projects and (La)TeX documents or macros.</p>
</p>
